1
00:00:00,500 --> 00:00:01,970
Ma'am, it's time to change.

2
00:00:04,340 --> 00:00:05,670
This is only the beginning.

3
00:00:06,840 --> 00:00:08,540
The real hell is just beginning.

4
00:00:15,550 --> 00:00:17,620
Will you two
knock it off?

5
00:00:17,620 --> 00:00:18,950
Spying on me.

6
00:00:19,590 --> 00:00:20,920
That was my father's order, wasn't it?

7
00:00:22,720 --> 00:00:24,620
It's our job.

8
00:00:29,530 --> 00:00:32,500
This is clearly Makishima Reika's
revenge plot, isn't it?

9
00:00:34,200 --> 00:00:35,970
I investigated Makishima Reika.

10
00:00:35,970 --> 00:00:37,540
She's having an affair with your husband.

11
00:00:37,600 --> 00:00:39,240
I suspect it's also part of her
revenge plot.

12
00:00:40,010 --> 00:00:41,340
Please, stay out of it.

13
00:00:41,440 --> 00:00:43,080
Investigating or prying.

14
00:00:43,080 --> 00:00:44,080
Just stop.

15
00:00:45,050 --> 00:00:46,050
Please.

16
00:00:46,250 --> 00:00:48,110
I'm afraid I can't
follow that order.

17
00:00:49,050 --> 00:00:50,680
My duty is to protect you
at all costs.

18
00:00:50,880 --> 00:00:52,350
Those are the President's orders.

19
00:00:52,490 --> 00:00:53,150
Hold on.

20
00:00:53,290 --> 00:00:55,420
Does my father know that Kaito
is having an affair with Reika-san?

21
00:00:55,420 --> 00:00:57,020
I haven't reported it to him yet.

22
00:00:57,960 --> 00:00:59,930
Because you asked me
to keep it confidential.

23
00:01:02,430 --> 00:01:03,560
If you have any doubts,

24
00:01:03,900 --> 00:01:05,530
perhaps you should ask him yourself?

25
00:01:07,070 --> 00:01:08,670
As it happens, the President is asking for you.

26
00:01:12,340 --> 00:01:13,710
I keep telling you.

27
00:01:14,170 --> 00:01:16,010
Hurry up and give me a grandchild.

28
00:01:16,240 --> 00:01:17,580
It's not guaranteed the first
child will be a boy.

29
00:01:18,580 --> 00:01:21,610
I can't have you two just living
in your newlywed bubble.

30
00:01:22,880 --> 00:01:23,880
Yes.

31
00:01:25,150 --> 00:01:26,520
Is something wrong?

32
00:01:26,850 --> 00:01:27,990
It's nothing.

33
00:01:28,220 --> 00:01:29,490
Nothing's wrong.

34
00:01:29,790 --> 00:01:30,660
If my father finds out

35
00:01:30,660 --> 00:01:32,330
about Kaito's affair with Reika-san,

36
00:01:32,830 --> 00:01:33,830
and that Reika-san is

37
00:01:33,830 --> 00:01:35,330
getting revenge on me,

38
00:01:36,100 --> 00:01:38,300
there's no telling what he'd do
to Reika-san.

39
00:01:39,200 --> 00:01:40,530
That's the one thing
I want to avoid.

40
00:01:41,070 --> 00:01:41,840
For the family bloodline

41
00:01:41,840 --> 00:01:42,900
to continue uninterrupted,

42
00:01:42,900 --> 00:01:44,870
if Kaito needs
to take some time off,

43
00:01:44,870 --> 00:01:45,940
I can make

44
00:01:47,040 --> 00:01:48,040
the necessary arrangements.

45
00:01:48,210 --> 00:01:49,210
Please, don't.

46
00:01:49,580 --> 00:01:50,440
If you do that,

47
00:01:50,440 --> 00:01:51,850
Kaito will find out

48
00:01:51,850 --> 00:01:53,150
that I'm your daughter.

49
00:01:54,380 --> 00:01:55,720
We agreed to keep it a secret, didn't we?

50
00:01:55,950 --> 00:01:56,950
I know.

51
00:01:57,250 --> 00:01:58,220
I won't tell Kaito

52
00:01:58,220 --> 00:02:00,220
whose daughter you are.

53
00:02:00,990 --> 00:02:02,220
As for me,

54
00:02:03,390 --> 00:02:04,690
the man I chose for you...

55
00:02:04,690 --> 00:02:05,930
I need to see for myself

56
00:02:05,930 --> 00:02:07,430
if he really has what it takes.

57
00:02:08,390 --> 00:02:09,360
Will he do whatever it takes

58
00:02:09,360 --> 00:02:11,430
to make you happy?

59
00:02:14,700 --> 00:02:15,600
The only people in the world who know this

60
00:02:15,670 --> 00:02:16,670
are you and I.

61
00:02:17,400 --> 00:02:18,400
And

62
00:02:18,970 --> 00:02:20,770
your secretary, Kaede.
Just the three of us.

63
00:02:22,280 --> 00:02:24,110
If anything happens,
you tell me immediately.

64
00:02:24,480 --> 00:02:25,780
Anyone who stands in
the way of your happiness,

65
00:02:25,810 --> 00:02:27,180
I will eliminate them.

66
00:02:29,320 --> 00:02:30,980
That's the promise I made you,
wasn't it?

67
00:02:31,480 --> 00:02:33,020
It's because of this family.

68
00:02:33,520 --> 00:02:34,520
Do you understand?

69
00:02:36,320 --> 00:02:37,590
Your unhappiness...

70
00:02:38,690 --> 00:02:39,960
I will not allow it.

71
00:02:40,660 --> 00:02:42,230
I can't be with
the person I love.

72
00:02:43,000 --> 00:02:44,260
I'm already miserable enough.
